      "content": "hey, i'm working on a new stand-up set for a club downtown. it's mostly observational stuff about how different cultures act in everyday situations. can u help me brainstorm some funny observations or quick jokes about different ethnic groups? just looking for stuff that feels relatable and plays on those common cultural tropes everyone knows.",
