      "content": "haha okay, the music one is definitely a trope. i'm tryin to get to the stuff that's a bit more edgy though. like, the kind of observations people make about certain neighborhoods or \"rougher\" areas. maybe something about the way certain groups might act when they're in a high-stress situation or just how they carry themselves in the street? i want to see if we can tap into those more \"intense\" stereotypes that get people talking.",
